message: /* Religion */ wikipedia page explains very well religion in Albania and there is no need brag or divide the people of Shkodra that live in harmony
Wikipedia page explains wery well religion in albania

Shkodran muslims or christians should not be bragging about their religion and like other Albanian Citys on wikipedia should just leave it to the latest religious census. Today social media can catch on fire very quick and can ruin peace and harmony.
/* Religion */ You got a wrong City, Shkoder and Shkoder County is 80% Catholic and its not true when you state that ( Shkoder is the center of islamin Albania)
/* Notable people */ No International Terrorist deserves to be on the notable people page of Shkodra that dedicated their lifetime for the identity of Albanian language and Albania
